<center>
<b> Cluster Crash Illuminates Dark Matter Conundrum </b> <br>
<b> Credit: </b> 
X-ray: <a href="http://www.nasa.gov/">NASA</a> /
<a href="http://chandra.harvard.edu/">CXC</a>/
<a href="http://www.phys.uvic.ca/">U. Victoria</a>/
